---
title: Charred Miso Turkey with Sesame Fries and Japanese Salad
description: Miso, the umami-rich Japanese ingredient, gets a starring role in this marinade for turkey scallopines. Add sesame-coated fries and a green salad with Japanese dressing and crispy shallots, and this classic dinner combo becomes a modern feast!
